data.description: Welcome to your next home located in the Meadows At Kyle community. This home features all sides masonry with 3 sides stone and hardi-plank siding on the back, including gutters around the entire perimeter. This popular single story 'Maple' floor plan has a recently painted interior. The primary bedroom is located at the rear of the home offering plenty of privacy with windows to the backyard. Relax on the covered back patio that overlooks the freshly sodded backyard with a view of pasture instead of another neighbor looking back at you. Cool off at the community pool located about 3 blocks from the house. Located convenient to I-35 for those commuting to Austin or San Marcos. Kyle Crossing shopping center is nearby with several big stores, HEB, restaurants, and entertainment. Charming old town Kyle is being revitalized with new shopping, entertainment, and restaurants, all slated to open soon! Kyle is primed to experience positive growth brought on by the substantial amount of planned development thats in the works. All appliances convey including the refrigerator and washer & dryer.
